{
  "stem": "13141.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We only hoped, you know, that-- our problem was that the bombs were dropped too far in, because they were afraid to drop them too close to us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were dropped pretty far in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But later on, when we started to advance, we saw the damage those bombs had achieved.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, well, I was with the third army-- with Patton's army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were the 204th Artillery Battalion, was attached to the 20th Corps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had the 90th Infantry Division and the 20th Corps, and other tank divisions, armored divisions, and the infantry divisions.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before our battle inside, it took us about-- about six weeks to break out of Normandy, because that's a peninsula, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't get out of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was near-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] near Arromanches, where we broke out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were many casualties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had children prisoners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah, I was unofficially interrogating children prisoners, because they always called me, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- Did your company know that you were a Jew?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in a battery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the field artillery, they called them Batteries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is a Company in the infantry, is a Battery in the artillery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[DRINKS] No.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must say, they took me-- they-- my commanding officer knew it, but even-- and some other knew it too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But strangely to say, they always took me more for a German than for a Jew, yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is also the reason that, as I found out later on when we had a get-together with my outfit after the war-- a few years ago we got together, a reunion, you know, of the 204th Field Artillery Battalion-- and I said, listen, I mean, I thought I was a good computer.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My commanding officer said, yes, I knew it, Richard.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
